      "description": "Now we're going to walk through a number of exercises that are outlined in this file (`asnake_exercises.md`).\n\n💡Tip: If you want to preview this file in a more reader-friendly format, you can right click the file name in the file explorer to the left and select \"Open Preview.\"\n\nWhen you've reached this point, raise your hand and select \"Finish Tour.\"",
